The Future of Computer Science Computer Science, Software Engineering and Information Systems are international qualifications, enabling people to work globally, and in a very broad variety of roles. 
There is steady growth in demand for technically adept and flexible IT graduates. Declining student enrollment, while growth continues in law, medicine, biology, economics, and business. 
The decline among women is particularly alarming. 
computer science essays Computer science is one of the fastest growing career fields in modern history. 
Dating back only a few decades to the late 1950s and early 1960s, it has become one of the leading industries in the world today. 